          "Their sum $A+B=\\begin{pmatrix}0&1\\\\1&0\\end{pmatrix}$ has $\\chi(x)=x^2-1$, eigenvalues $+1,-1$ — nonzero. Hence spectral nilpotency is *not* preserved under addition. $\\blacksquare$",
