          "This linear recurrence has characteristic roots $e^{\\pm i\\pi/3}$ (primitive $6$th roots of unity), so $\\{d_n\\}$ is **periodic with period $6$**: $d_n=1,1,0,-1,-1,0,1,1,0,\\dots$ for $n=0,1,2,3,4,5,\\dots$",
