          "For each $i$, AM–GM gives $\\sqrt{(1+s_i)(1-s_i)}\\le\\frac{(1+s_i)+(1-s_i)}{2}=1$ (the factors are $\\ge0$ since $s_i\\in[-1,1]$), hence $(1+s_i)(1-s_i)\\le1$.",
