          "Therefore $\\det M=\\prod_i\\lambda_i=1\\cdot2\\cdot2\\cdot4\\cdot4\\cdot5=320$. Since $\\det M=\\tau(\\widetilde{\\Sigma})$ by the Matrix-Tree theorem, the cover has $\\boxed{320}$ spanning trees, and $320=2^6\\cdot5$ records the two-sheet structure transparently."
